            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/nexus_svc" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.snapchat.com/add/nexus_svc" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-snapchat-square"></i></a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column col-md-12">
        <div class="question">
          <p>
            Will there be any accomodation facility for the participants from the college side?
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="answer">
          <p>
            No, we do not provide any kind of accomodations.

          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="column col-md-12">
        <div class="question">
          <p>
            How can a participant register for any event?
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="answer">
          <p>
            For registration in Formal Events, the willing participants need to check the Facebook page of particular society of whose event they wish to take participate in. <br>
            For registration in Informal Events the willing participants need to check the Facebook page of Nexus and fill registration form for that particular informal event. They can also register at the main desk in the college on the fest day.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
